comments: Harris (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball the ball from Booker (PHX).
Barton (DEN) takes a legal dribble during his move on the perimeter.
Harris (DEN) grasps Booker's (PHX) jersey off ball and affects his FOM.  This causes Booker to dislodge Harris in an attempt to disengage from the illegal contact.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact to Oubre Jr. (PHX) that does not affect his trajectory during the jump shot attempt.
Millsap (DEN) moves alongside of Bridges (PHX) during his drive to the basket but as Bridges goes up for the shot attempt, Millsap turns into him and initiates contact.
Jokic (DEN) makes a legal move before releasing the pass.
Baynes (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Barton (DEN) and absorbs the contact.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact to Booker (PHX) that does not affect his trajectory during his jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) releases from contact with Baynes (PHX) prior to his shot attempt.
Grant (DEN) cleanly blocks Booker (PHX) during his jump shot attempt.
